Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value:
BEGIN SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED SET NOCOUNT ON
SELECT DBTS = (CONVERT(BIGINT,MIN_ACTIVE_ROWVERSION())-1); END

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: BEGIN SELECT codHospital ,nombre ,ciudad ,telefono ,codMedicoDirector FROM Hospital WHERE [rowversion] > CONVERT(ROWVERSION,@startRow) AND [rowversion] <= CONVERT(ROWVERSION,@endRow) END

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value:
BEGIN SELECT codMedico ,DNI ,apellidosnombre ,fechaNacimiento ,hos.nombre
FROM Medico med INNER JOIN Hospital hos ON (med.codHospital=hos.codHospital) WHERE (med.[rowversion]) > CONVERT(ROWVERSION,@startRow) AND (med.[rowversion]) <= CONVERT(ROWVERSION,@endRow) OR (hos.[rowversion]) > CONVERT(ROWVERSION,@startRow) AND (hos.[rowversion]) <= CONVERT(ROWVERSION,@endRow) END

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: BEGIN SELECT codPaciente ,DNI ,apellidosnombre ,fechaNacimiento ,numSS ,datosOpcionales FROM Paciente WHERE [rowversion] > CONVERT(ROWVERSION,@startRow) AND [rowversion] <= CONVERT(ROWVERSION,@endRow) END

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: BEGIN SELECT codServicio ,nombre ,comentario FROM Servicio WHERE [rowversion] > CONVERT(ROWVERSION,@startRow) AND [rowversion] <= CONVERT(ROWVERSION,@endRow) END
